samples.commui
Class UserPassView

java.lang.Object
  samples.ui.View
      samples.commui.CommunityView
          samples.commui.UserPassView

public class UserPassView
extends CommunityView

UserPassView is a screen for capturing a user's username and password for new account creation. It contains one username entry field and two password entry fields ("password" and "confirm password"). Username is displayed in plaintext, while passwords are masked.

Input restrictions are listed in the comments for the validate() method.

Method Detail

validate

protected boolean validate()
Validates username and password entries according to the following rules:
  • Valid characters for username: alphanumeric and underscore. No spaces.
  • Valid characters for passwords: all ASCII values from 32-126.
  • Usernames and passwords must be 4-15 characters long, and cannot match.
  • Password and confirm password entries must match

Returns:
true if input validates
